Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你来拜访 我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.00,0:02:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是到底有什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把东西放在那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.80,0:03:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为太繁忙 差点就忘记了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是生日一定得选最好的礼物送你才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.90,0:03:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生日?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.30,0:03:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全是我挑选的好礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尺寸当然也没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的事没有什么是我不知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兰德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.00,0:03:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在讨论尺寸之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你犯了最基本的错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的生日是3月14日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道现在是几月吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是7月呀 7月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算你忘记了也不该这么离谱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是 不是 明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我是来向你讨礼物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.20,0:04:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能得到「你和我共度一段时光」的礼物吗
