Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这只一定比较适合呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兰德尔 你太过分啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是身为你的朋友来和你庆祝生日的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你的玩笑太过分的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就回去了
