Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我来说 现在是最佳机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想错过这个机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,机会?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你和隼人吵架了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.30,0:04:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么 你对他会失望是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的时候很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.20,0:05:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好的时候就拿旁人出气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连自己犯错也不承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,任性 傲慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身为车手或者身为男子汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他那种是最差劲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兰德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被那种家伙摆弄 斥责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我实在是看不下去
