Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我太多嘴了
