Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对赛车是门外汉的我不该对赛车的事过问的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你讲的话并没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.20,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是有没有错的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.10,0:05:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,车队和媒体已经给隼人很大压力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.40,0:05:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不该再说那种给隼人添加压力的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我应该说你也变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想要对他更温柔体贴是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.60,0:06:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这种东西对现在的他毫无帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之我是无所谓
