Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.80,0:06:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他丧失了身为车手最重要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.40,0:06:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到连你也没有发现这点
