Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第四个优胜落空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利兹的AL-ZARD进入工作站了
