Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是难以相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.00,0:07:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他使用的是生化计算机嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.10,0:07:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,单靠换个系统就能使车手能变成超人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当老板就不用那么辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,2018年最后一战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在预赛里突破风见隼人的极速纪录时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.40,0:07:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的吼声我是不会忘记的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是你和极限搏斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在和你的极限挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.80,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在高速的恐惧与赌上所有一切的吼声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连经验和技术一流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,位于顶尖车手行列的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要跑出那种速度都那么困难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管再怎样进化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是改了个向导系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.30,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就可以使一个新人轻易达到那种速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,世上有这么荒谬的事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我输你一筹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 我们的确不是傀儡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会犯错 会感到恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是他什么错也不犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连跑的路线都丝毫不紊乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每次都露出轻松的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.70,0:08:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要说奇怪 确实是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙是机器人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛 干嘛真的打呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,游戏是游戏 比赛是比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!既然那样 我也不手下留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.70,0:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,120,!Effect,{}美国 佛罗里达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂! 等一下 把球还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.30,0:09:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他丧失了身为车手最重要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到连你也没有发现这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你回来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都玩得很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃...我知道训练很重要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但偶尔也该散散心嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难得哥哥排出时间给你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我又没说我需要放假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想玩的是明日香你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在我没有时间悠闲地度假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,车队也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.30,0:10:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来散心又怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在海边玩又改不了车子性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在我们玩的时候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟你抱怨也是没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.80,0:10:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么去看车赛好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.90,0:10:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,车赛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么车赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我听说新条也有出场哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.90,0:10:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是普通汽车赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,普通汽车?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美琪写信过来有提到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊!果然是今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.90,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不去 我没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.50,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,普通赛车和我赛车的类别完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看了也没什么收获
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是... 新条也有出场啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也很久没见到美琪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你叫我和他们见面叙旧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.30,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以我现在的成绩搞不好还会遭到嘲笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.20,0:11:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了 算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.70,0:11:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那么讨厌放假的话就快滚回日本去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,浪费大家的假期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家担心你 看你脸色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经受够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的手晒得好红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不快涂防晒油就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的饭一直没收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌!拉链卡住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.10,0:12:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个...不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎可以...请温柔点...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肥婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.50,0:12:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,120,!Effect,{}佛罗里达州 迪特拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,车号26 史蒂芬·福利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追上来的是车号8号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前年的冠军 杰法·金格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.40,0:12:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,换了车队以后自信满满的奥里巴利也占到了好位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.30,0:12:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后是最近渐入佳境的车号48
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前高智能方程式冠军 日本的新条直辉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剩下8圈 各车正在加速了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我说太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.60,0:13:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,48号车新条的车子一直追上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,挤进领先的车群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.60,0:13:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那...真的是新条?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那时候古雷格真是太丢脸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 可不会这样就玩完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一场比赛会赢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交给新条就十拿九稳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 让你们来这么吵的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是我们打扰你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别客气 还要谢谢你们来看我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在放假吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我记得第四战才刚结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.50,0:14:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺他怎样了?是不是瘫在一边一直发牢骚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是有讲类似的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.70,0:14:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说要是我也被开除就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.90,0:14:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以他的性格我早料到会那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美琪你变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新条也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗?真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许我变得更壮一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁叫他让我在这里经历了那么多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.10,0:14:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 为什么要参加普通汽车赛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.00,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以新条的资历\N大可以去任何优秀的高智能方程式队啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.20,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.90,0:15:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直辉一开始也像加贺一样喊着要参加奖金车赛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.90,0:15:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直辉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.30,0:15:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美琪说那毕竟太鲁莽了 阻止了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.80,0:15:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美琪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奖金车赛...为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎样说好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.40,0:15:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我想把过去的自己全部抛开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直辉是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.30,0:15:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想到什么就一股脑完全往那边冲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起哦 我就是笨嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.40,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是因为那部AL-ZARD和弗利兹的出现而被解雇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.90,0:15:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,名云社长当时指出了我许多缺点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.70,0:15:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当时我无法坦白承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想如果我驾驶那部车我也会赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.10,0:15:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,觉得到这里赛车的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚开始我也是满脑子想车子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,认为没有性能好的车的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这时候我被美琪大骂了一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.00,0:16:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.70,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有说啊 你说「你没有好车就无法开车了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.10,0:16:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样不就表示你的头脑与技术都没用啰？」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我没说错吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 车子性能好的话 连一年级的学生都能跑赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是赛车是那样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是制造高速车的游戏竞赛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是那种东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.10,0:16:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的确为了取胜 或许要有跑得快的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是车赛不光是看车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,驾驶的人是我们呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是职业车手的我在驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以玩普通汽车也不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.90,0:16:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为那绝对是靠车手的技术决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且也不太需要花钱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过去我跑的诸多车赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我绝对不是跑不赢比赛的车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.80,0:17:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当我有信心去克服\N一切恶劣条件和车子性能差异的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会回到高智能方程式赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.70,0:17:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后击败他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人 到时候直辉会很强喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.20,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使是你 或许也不会那样轻易取胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.10,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...一定要向你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在巴西时对你说的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有其它很多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.90,0:18:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...到底一直在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我根本不是在比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是开车而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.30,0:18:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我被AL-ZARD凌驾之后 非常焦急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿大家当出气筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.00,0:18:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.80,0:18:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在新条面前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.80,0:18:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我完全不敢正视他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是 看着你痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我却什么也帮不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我或许是在逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.00,0:18:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心想这始终只是隼人你的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我应该更认真地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你一起想办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像美琪那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.90,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你会原谅我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.70,0:19:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切都是你非赢不可的心情引发出来的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.10,0:19:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.60,0:19:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样的演出效果用在和解的结局上是太过火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.80,0:20:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风见5.2秒就离开工作站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在以第六的排名回到车道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,领先的仍是葵的菲尔·弗利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.20,0:20:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二位是卡尔·里胥特·冯·兰德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第三位是法兰兹·海尼尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟着是加贺和古力特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那后面是风见隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利兹跑到第48圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.30,0:20:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来西班牙杯的优胜又是他的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!今天就由我来掩护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前辈....请等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我掩护你呀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是车赛不光是看车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,驾驶的人是我们呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是职业车手的我在驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.60,0:21:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 我也不是只靠车子性能和运气拿下两个冠军的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追上了 要去了!阿斯拉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人那家伙今天气势这么强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌的家伙到前面来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.20,0:21:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有了 转弯的地方有出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.90,0:21:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.80,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也很不愿指责 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又是雷欧·安哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.30,0:21:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,波及到了竞争第四的加贺和风见的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.30,0:21:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样三辆车都要退出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.00,0:21:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这个大饭桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.60,0:21:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干脆断手算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是为了世人好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.60,0:22:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我实在是输给那个新人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.90,0:22:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他非把别人拖下水才高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.80,0:22:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.50,0:22:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今日子小姐呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.50,0:22:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.60,0:22:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她刚才和名云社长在那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.20,0:22:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在车房里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.50,0:22:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有人在吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.80,0:22:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今日子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.70,0:22:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真难得 这里竟然一个人也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.70,0:22:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么啊 从没看过的饮料？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.70,0:22:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.20,0:22:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.20,0:23:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.60,0:23:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这家伙真现实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.60,0:23:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一和明日香和好就马上变得这么有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别说奇怪的话好吗? 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.40,0:23:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别生气 别生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 你有没有看见今日子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.00,0:23:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才我看见她向驾驶沙龙的方向去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.40,0:23:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗? 那么我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 隼人 拿一瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.90,0:23:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.70,0:23:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.10,0:23:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是营养饮料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.00,0:23:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没体力是会被明日香讨厌喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.50,0:23:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.80,0:23:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.00,0:23:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贺不论什么时候都很匆忙的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.70,0:23:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.10,0:23:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.50,0:23:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难得有这段空闲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.90,0:23:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起去吃好吃的东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.50,0:23:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赞成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.00,0:24:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么 难喝死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.30,0:24:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果还是弗利兹胜出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.40,0:24:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 那家伙真的很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.80,0:24:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要快点想办法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.30,0:24:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人!你开得太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.60,0:24:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不应该啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.60,0:24:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.10,0:24:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样真的可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.00,0:24:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.70,0:24:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是你还是小心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.20,0:24:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次发现就不能放过你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.40,0:24:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.00,0:24:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.40,0:25:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我并没有打算要开那么快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.00,0:25:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还以为是80公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.60,0:25:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说那是80公里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.00,0:25:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别开玩笑!速度表都快爆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.90,0:25:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.40,0:25:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的速度感觉应该没错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.20,0:25:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之换我来开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.50,0:25:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了 下次我会小心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.70,0:25:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.10,0:25:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香 我肚子饿扁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.80,0:25:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.90,0:25:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在小心开车 别啰嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.70,0:25:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 比乌龟还要慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.30,0:25:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明日香 你在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.20,0:25:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使我稍微跟你开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.70,0:25:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也不要这么乱来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.00,0:25:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,减速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:58.40,0:25:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.20,0:26:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停车!!停车!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.00,0:26:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隼人!你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.90,0:26:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,振作点 隼人
